# Frontend Homelab Environment Variables
# Note: NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are baked at Docker build time, not runtime.
#
# With subdomain routing, the frontend is served at the root of each subdomain:
#   Staging:    https://staging-ptt.nurulizyansyaza.com
#   Production: https://ptt.nurulizyansyaza.com
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=/api (same-origin, relative URL)
# No basePath needed — frontend is at root of subdomain
